# Beginning Sailing Lesson windows, by weekday, for the Cal Sailing Club event.
#
# The dashboard shows the OVERLAP of these hours with the club's actual
# open/close times (live-scraped). A weekday with no entry here = no lessons =
# no event. If tides make the club open late, past a window, that day's event is
# suppressed automatically (e.g. a Saturday where the club opens at 1:30 PM).
#
# Format (whitespace-separated, 24-hour HH:MM):
#   <weekday> <start> <end> [<dst_start> <dst_end>]
#
# weekday: full or 3-letter, case-insensitive (Mon, Monday, ...).
# The optional dst_start/dst_end replace start/end while Daylight Saving Time is
# in effect (Pacific zone). '#' comments and blank lines are ignored. Multiple
# lines for the same weekday are allowed (each becomes its own window).
#
# Cal Sailing beginning lessons: Mon & Thu afternoons (1-4 PM; 1-5 PM during
# DST), and Sat mornings (10 AM-1 PM).
Monday    13:00 16:00  13:00 17:00
Thursday  13:00 16:00  13:00 17:00
Saturday  10:00 13:00
